  "_patches_note": "Exp-B 성공 시: INF TextReplace 3개 + AddReg TextReplace 1개. Exp-C 성공 시: 위 + amdgcf.dat BinaryInsert 추가.",
  "patches": [
	{
	  "type": "TextReplace",
	  "file": "u0201163.inf",
	  "search": "\"%AMD7340.45%\" = ati2mtag_Navi14, PCI\\VEN_1002&DEV_7340&REV_CF",
	  "replacement": "\"%AMD7340.45%\" = ati2mtag_Navi14, PCI\\VEN_1002&DEV_7340&REV_CF\r\n\"%AMD7340.46%\" = ati2mtag_Navi14, PCI\\VEN_1002&DEV_7340&SUBSYS_020F106B&REV_40",
	  "expectedOccurrences": 1
	},
	{
	  "type": "TextReplace",
	  "file": "u0201163.inf",
	  "search": "AMD7340.45 = \"Radeon RX 5300\"",
	  "replacement": "AMD7340.45 = \"Radeon RX 5300\"\r\nAMD7340.46 = \"AMD Radeon Pro 5500M\"",
	  "expectedOccurrences": 1
	},
	{
	  "type": "TextReplace",
	  "file": "u0201163.inf",
	  "search": "ExcludeID = PCI\\VEN_1002&DEV_7340&SUBSYS_020F106B",
	  "replacement": "; Boot Camp override: PCI\\VEN_1002&DEV_7340&SUBSYS_020F106B",
	  "expectedOccurrences": 3
	},
	{
	  "_comment": "아래 AddReg 패치는 Exp-B 실험용입니다. 실제 INF의 [ati2mtag_Navi14.HW] 섹션 텍스트를 확인하고 search 값을 맞춰야 합니다.",
	  "type": "TextReplace",
	  "file": "u0201163.inf",
	  "search": "REPLACE_WITH_EXACT_HW_SECTION_TEXT_FROM_INF",
	  "replacement": "REPLACE_WITH_EXACT_HW_SECTION_TEXT_FROM_INF\r\n\r\n[AMD7340.46.HW]\r\nAddReg = AMD7340.46.BootCamp.AddReg\r\n\r\n[AMD7340.46.BootCamp.AddReg]\r\nHKR,,KMD_BootCampPlatform,0x00010001,1\r\nHKR,,PP_Apple_Bootcamp_Enable,0x00010001,1\r\nHKR,,KMD_EnableDisplayableSupport,0x00010001,0\r\nHKR,,EnableUlps,0x00010001,0\r\nHKR,,PP_GfxOffControl,0x00010001,0\r\nHKR,,DalPSRFeatureEnable,0x00010001,0\r\nHKR,,KMD_EnableBrightnessInterface2,0x00010001,0\r\nHKR,,UseExecuteIndirectPacket,0x00010001,0\r\nHKR,,PP_Falcon_QuickTransition_Enable,0x00010001,1\r\nHKR,,MobileLinkOverCloudAuth_NA,0x00010001,0",
	  "expectedOccurrences": 1
	}
  ],
